            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Top, tail, peel and grate the <strong>carrot<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong>, then peel and finely chop (or grate) the <strong>shallots</strong></p><p>Grate the<strong> apple<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong>, then tear or chop the <strong>little gem</strong> into bite-sized pieces</p><p>Add the above to a mixing bowl and give it a good mix up – this is your <strong>slaw salad</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
